Installation guide
==================

1) System wide installation

To install into a directory accessible for all users
you must have root/wheel access.

Procedure:
$ perl Build.PL
$ ./Build
$ sudo ./Build install


2) Installation in own home directory

This is useful when testing out the software. Of course
this do *not* require any root/wheel access.

Procedure:
$ perl Build.PL --install_base=~
$ ./Build
$ ./Build install

